{"tid":388922,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟約女仔出街應該去邊？","createTime":"2017-09-05T19:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T19:41:06.000Z","uid":118211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8384b4638a8296246ad588ad4e7af2f11abd0417","tid":388922,"uid":118211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:09:44.000Z","msg":"朋友借ac問<br />\n最近識咗個絲打,但本身自己只係會行下模型舖,耳機舖同食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上自己又唔鍾意睇戲.好擔心約佢去街會悶到佢.<br />\n想問下有冇餐廳同玩樂活動介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059492a1c1542ef8223687a23f6a39c2ab671c21","tid":388922,"uid":278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"時鐘酒店 大家互動實唔會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實主題公園最無敵"},{"pid":"dc515bedc4a0ed17ad9f8e842fa2bd0c24322f3a","tid":388922,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:17:29.000Z","msg":"第一次出街帶佢去食甜品順便傾下計了解下對方"},{"pid":"5295e12a90dfeeb8521b4bffd4fd518e4823a7b0","tid":388922,"uid":118211,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時鐘酒店 大家互動實唔會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實主題公園最無敵</blockquote><br />\n你個咸濕仔!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係對佢有好感嘅(其實唔至好感),但第一次去街就去主題公園,我怕佢會知我係想發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有我好驚海_公園.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個小學同朋友去哈__嚇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想第一次出街傾多小小自己嘅野,留意多啲佢嘅大小事.再試下去其他地方"},{"pid":"4513996b21ecfa1c2585be62124740db11e7e949","tid":388922,"uid":118211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017